  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.9">
<l>ēḻulakun tāḻvaraiyu meṅku mūṭi yeṇṭicaiyu maṇṭalamum maṇṭi yaṇṭam</l>
<l>mōḻaiyeḻun tāḻimiku mūḻi veḷḷam muṉṉakaṭṭi loṭukkiyavem mūrtti kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>ūḻitoṟu mūḻitoṟu muyarnta celvat tōṅkiyanāṉ maṟaiyaṉaittun tāṅku nāvar</l>
<l>cēḻuyarnta maṇimāṭan tikaḻum nāṅkūrt tiruteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our god who long ago enclosed in his belly an apocalyptic flood</l>
<l rend="indent">when the sea swelled, rising from subterranean waters,</l>
<l>Rushing [over] the eight directions, areas of land, and the earth,</l>
<l rend="indent">covering the seven worlds, sloped mountains, and everywhere, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where shine jeweled mansions where stories rise</l>
<l>Of those whose tongues bear the entirety of the four Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">whose bounty, which rises from each eon to each eon, increases.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
